### Test SAMIT Backend API
### Server: https://localhost:5002

### 1. Test Server Status
GET https://localhost:5002/api/users/login
Accept: application/json

### 2. Import Excel File
POST https://localhost:5002/api/assets/import-excel
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="UPDATE ASET FEB 2026 Rev01.xlsx"
Content-Type: application/vnd.openxmlformats-officedocument.spreadsheetml.sheet

< /path/to/UPDATE ASET FEB 2026 Rev01.xlsx >
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="debug"

1
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

### 3. List Assets (Requires Auth)
GET https://localhost:5002/api/assets
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
Accept: application/json
